data.description: Sleek & stylish modern home on a large quarter-acre corner lot in the sought-after Point Venture lakefront community! Nestled along Lake Travis' serene north shore, this area exudes perpetual holiday vibes, favoring golf carts for transportation. Built in 2021, this 4BD/2.5BA contemporary gem radiates freshness, adorned with exquisite designer touches. Featuring vaulted ceilings graced by stained wood beams, a chic wall-mounted electric fireplace, and gorgeous wood-inspired luxury vinyl plank floors. Entertaining here is a breeze with the open floor plan and inviting breakfast bar seating. The impressive chef-inspired gourmet kitchen features timeless shaker-style cabinetry, quartz countertops, and high-end SS appliances that are sure to please the home chef. The secluded main floor primary suite will serve as your peaceful getaway, while the luxury ensuite bathroom will serve as your daily spa retreat with the built-in soaking tub, large walk-in shower, and walk-in closet. Upstairs you will find 3 bright & spacious secondary bedrooms and a gorgeous full secondary bathroom complete with a dual vanity. Outside, the covered back porch invites relaxation against Point Venture's backdrop. The backyard is primed for personalization and provides a manicured sod lawn embraced by a grove of shade trees that create a natural privacy screen. Excellent Lago Vista schools! Point Venture residents relish community luxuries—a 9-hole golf course, Jr Olympic-sized pool, tennis and pickleball courts, marina access, and a private 50-acre waterfront park with a sandy beach. A fitness center, floating restaurant, library, and playground enrich the lifestyle. Beyond, the Balcones Canyonlands National Wildlife Refuge offers hiking trails amidst breathtaking landscapes. Just 20 miles from Cedar Park's retail hub and an hour from Downtown Austin, this contemporary gem is impeccably priced and primed for your personal touch. Seize the opportunity to make it your own today!
